3 §3173. Powers of the Board of Regents; coordination with management boards
4 A. In coordination with each management board of a public
5 postsecondary institution, the Board of Regents shall have the power to set
6 policy regarding each of the following:
7 (1) Accreditation of public postsecondary institutions.
8 (2) Specialized accreditation of any individual program or unit at a
9 public postsecondary institution where such accreditation is required.
